com.example.buber.Model

Class ApplicationModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • com.example.buber.Model.ApplicationModel

  • public class ApplicationModel
extends java.util.Observable
    Root class for our application data. Contains all needed data that views require. Extends the Observable class to implement MVC. Contains data like current user, current trip (if one exists), query results and mapstate.
